Enumeration Case# Loading

A value that indicates the Look Around view is loading.MapKit JS 5.79+

```
readonly Loading: "loading";
```

## [See Also](/documentation/MapKitJS/LookAroundReadyState/Loading#see-also)

### [Look Around object states](/documentation/MapKitJS/LookAroundReadyState/Loading#Look-Around-object-states)

[`Complete`](/documentation/mapkitjs/lookaroundreadystate/complete)A value that indicates the Look Around view has completed loading.[`Destroyed`](/documentation/mapkitjs/lookaroundreadystate/destroyed)A value that indicates the Look Around object is destroyed.[`Error`](/documentation/mapkitjs/lookaroundreadystate/error)A value that indicates the Look Around view encountered an error while loading.
